import React, {useState} from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import {useParams} from "react-router-dom"; export function AddAddress(){ const [address, setAddress] = useState() const params= useParams() const submitresponse= (event) => { console.log(event.target.username) axios.post("http://localhost:9087/addAddress/"+params.userid,address) .then(response => {console.log(response)}) .catch(error => {console.log(error)}) event.preventDefault() } return(
{setAddress({...address,name:e.target.value})}}/>
{setAddress({...address,homenumber:e.target.value})}}/>
{setAddress({...address,area:e.target.value})}}/>
{setAddress({...address,state:e.target.value})}}/>
{setAddress({...address,pincode:e.target.value})}}/>
{setAddress({...address,phone:e.target.value})}}/>
) }
